      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in pristine, showroom condition, this vehicle exemplifies automotive excellence. Every facet of its maintenance history and aesthetic presentation has been meticulously curated to meet the highest standards of the discerning collector. An uncompromising example of its model, it offers a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber and mechanical integrity.",
